t</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/ru/docs/Web/API/Navigator\"><code>Navigator</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PageTransitionEvent\"><code>PageTransitionEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Plugin\"><code>Plugin</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PluginArray\"><code>PluginArray</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PopStateEvent\"><code>PopStateEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PromiseRejectionEvent\"><code>PromiseRejectionEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/RadioNodeList\"><code>RadioNodeList</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/ru/docs/Web/API/ValidityState\"><code>ValidityState</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ru/docs/Web/API/Window\"><code>Window</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<p>Обработчик для события загрузки&nbsp;объекта&nbsp;<a href=\"/ru/docs/Web/API/Window\"><code>window</code></a>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"Синтаксис","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"eval notranslate\">window.onload = <em>funcRef</em>;\n</pre>\n\n<ul>\n <li><code>funcRef</code> функция обработчик события будет вызвана, когда&nbsp;произойдёт событие загрузки окна.</li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"example","title":"Примеры","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code>window<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function-variable function\">onload</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token function\">init</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token function\">doSomethingElse</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token doctype\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;!</span><span class=\"token doctype-tag\">doctype</span> <span class=\"token name\">html</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>html</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>head</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>title</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>onload test<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>title</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>script</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token script\"><span class=\"token language-javascript\">\n      <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">load</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"token function\">alert</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"Событие загрузки поймано!\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n      window<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>onload <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> load<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    </span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>script</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>head</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>body</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Событие загрузки произойдёт, когда документ будет загружен!<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>body</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>html</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"notes","title":"Примечания","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Событие загрузки возникают в конце процесса загрузки документа. В этот момент все объекты документа находятся в DOM, и все картинки, скрипты, фреймы, ссылки загружены.</p>\n\n<p>Есть также&nbsp;<a href=\"/en-US/Gecko-Specific_DOM_Events\" title=\"en/Gecko-Specific_DOM_Events\">Gecko</a>&nbsp;события&nbsp;как&nbsp;<code>DOMContentLoaded</code>&nbsp;и&nbsp;<code>DOMFrameContentLoaded</code> (которые могут быть навешены с помощью <a href=\"/ru/docs/Web/API/EventTarget/addEventListener\"><code>EventTarget.addEventListener()</code></a>) которые возникают после&nbsp;того как DOM для страницы будет собран, но не ждут, когда другие ресурсы будут загружены.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specification","title":"Спецификации","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Этот обработчик события указан в стандарте&nbsp;<a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.whatwg.org/html/#handler-window-onload\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML</a>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"смотрите_также","title":"Смотрите также","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><code>DOMContentLoaded</code> событие в&nbsp;<a href=\"/en-US/Listening_to_events#simple_dom.c2.a0events\" title=\"En/Listening to events#Simple DOM.c2.a0events\">Listening to events: Simple DOM events</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Синтаксис","id":"syntax"},{"text":"Примеры","id":"example"},{"text":"Примечания","id":"notes"},{"text":"Спецификации","id":"specification"},{"text":"Смотрите также","id":"смотрите_также"}],"summary":"Обработчик для события загрузки объекта window.","popularity":0.0009,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"GlobalEventHandlers.onload","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch"},{"title":"GlobalEventHandlers.onload","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"window.onload","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"window.onload","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"GlobalEventHandlers.onload","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"window.onload","locale":"pl","native":"Polski"},{"title":"GlobalEventHandlers.onload","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"GlobalEventHandlers.onload","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"ru/web/api/globaleventhandlers/onload","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ru/web/api/globaleventhandlers/onload/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/ru/docs/Web","title":"Веб-технологии для разработчиков"},{"uri":"/ru/docs/Web/API","title":"Интерфейсы веб API"},{"uri":"/ru/docs/Web/API/GlobalEventHandlers","title":"GlobalEventHandlers"},{"uri":"/ru/docs/Web/API/GlobalEventHandlers/onload","title":"GlobalEventHandlers.onload"}],"pageTitle":"GlobalEventHandlers.onload - Интерфейсы веб API | MDN","noIndexing":false}}